- [Docker](/getting-started/docker) — Run NodeDB in containers

## Troubleshooting

**psql: connection refused**: Make sure NodeDB is running and listening on 127.0.0.1:6432.

**Collection not found**: Use `SHOW COLLECTIONS` to see what exists. Collections are created automatically on first INSERT or explicit CREATE COLLECTION.

**Vector search is slow**: Create a vector index with `CREATE VECTOR INDEX`. Without an index, search is O(n) brute force.

**Out of memory**: Reduce the `memory_limit` in server.toml or tune engine budget fractions in `[engines]`.
